skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: relationship tips
des: Users can now ask Alexa for tips on how to make their significant-other happy with slightly comical tones. Just say, "Alexa, open Relationship Tips." Or say "Alexa, tell relationship tips to give me advice. If you're having relationship issues, no sweat, Alexa's Relationship Tips skill will help steer you into greener pastures. This app also features fun and creative date ideas. Just say, "Alexa, ask relationship tips for good date ideas." Enjoy.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
